{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_MarineNoise}}
'''A_MarineNoise'''<br>
(no parameters)<br>

Plays the sound "weapons/sawidle" on the WEAPON channel if the calling actor's current weapon is [[SetMarineWeapon|set]] to the chainsaw.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|ScriptedMarine}} and derived classes.

